WEBVTT

1
00:35:04.000 --> 00:35:06.460 
有一次，他救了我一命
For once, he rescued me.

2
00:35:06.660 --> 00:35:09.670 
纽约 - 12月25日 - 1991

3
00:35:09.960 --> 00:35:12.050 
我依旧超支度日
I was still living way beyond my means.

4
00:35:12.090 --> 00:35:15.210 
房贷超高 以信用卡养信用卡
Mortgaged to the hilt, using one credit card to pay another.

5
00:35:15.650 --> 00:35:19.810 
我以前宠惯了她现在只好拼命想办法
Anything to keep Ava in the style to which she had thanks largely to me

6
00:35:19.870 --> 00:35:21.130 
才能维持她以往的生活水平
become accustomed.

7
00:35:22.290 --> 00:35:24.080 
艾娃，这太贵重了
Ava, this is too much.

8
00:35:24.110 --> 00:35:25.620 
尤里很宠爱你的
Yuri likes to spoil you.

9
00:35:25.680 --> 00:35:26.530 
突然间
Then suddenly,

10
00:35:26.560 --> 00:35:28.390 
我所有的圣诞礼物都一起来了
all my Christmases came at once.

11
00:35:28.410 --> 00:35:31.100 
尼奇，你会走啦!好孩子!
Nicki, you did it! Good boy!

12
00:35:31.140 --> 00:35:33.530 
这才像我孙子!
That's my grandson!

13
00:35:33.560 --> 00:35:35.820 
尤里，快来看你儿子在干嘛
Yuri, don't you want to see what your son is doing?

14
00:35:35.850 --> 00:35:38.100 
说施比受更有福的人
Whoever said it's better to give than receive...

